author: Shelbie
title: Can you pass the Mandela Effect memory test? (Quiz)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
The “Mandela Effect” is what the internet calls that weird phenomenon when many people swear to remember something a certain way only to find out that they’re all wrong. Some chalk it up to a coincidental case of collective bad memory, but other have gone as far to say that there might be an alternate dimension. Either way, use this quiz to determine if you’ve got a case of the Mandela Effect yourself!
